Package assignmentevaluator.evaluationHelpers.executors.classlevel

Class ClassTestExecutor

java.lang.Object
assignmentevaluator.evaluationHelpers.executors.TestExecutor
assignmentevaluator.evaluationHelpers.executors.classlevel.ClassTestExecutor
public abstract class ClassTestExecutor extends assignmentevaluator.evaluationHelpers.executors.TestExecutor
An abstract executor class responsible for evaluating a class-level test case. This class defines the structure and shared functionality required for running tests on a specific class file and handling the results.
